{"tid":2094883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"前京官稱鬥爭升級 預備「人幣美元脫鈎」","createTime":"2020-07-05T04:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T10:22:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":141,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"a634f26ed144effa93c535ad77ff337255a08e48","tid":2094883,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:47:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200705/MO4V33C7FJFP7ZFL7AJ3I4PDH4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200705%2FMO4V33C7FJFP7ZFL7AJ3I4PDH4%2F&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=6615ff41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200705%2FMO4V33C7FJFP7ZFL7AJ3I4PDH4%2F&h=8710cba9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200705/MO4V33C7FJFP7ZFL7AJ3I4PDH4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n前京官稱鬥爭升級 預備「人幣美元脫鈎」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZQs3CzJNZbIoj4awN_u6rglZ4IA=/541x383/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/34YN2HRUG3X3P753EDFRHVGPKQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZQs3CzJNZbIoj4awN_u6rglZ4IA%3D%2F541x383%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F34YN2HRUG3X3P753EDFRHVGPKQ.gif&h=876be3d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國現時面對嚴重內憂外患，中聯部前副部長周力公開希望官方要做好「六大準備」，包括中美關係惡化、產業鏈斷裂、人民幣（圖）及美元脫鈎及糧食危機等。<br />\n<br />\n周力在中國社科院主管雜誌《中國社會科學報》發表題為《積極主動應對外部環境變化》的文章，他認為現時世界經歷大變局，希望中國政府做好六大準備，分別是「做好中美關係惡化加劇、鬥爭全面升級的準備；要做好應對外部需求萎縮、產業鏈和供應鏈斷裂的準備；要做好新冠病毒疫情常態化、病毒與人類長期共存的準備；要做好擺脫美元霸權、逐步實現人民幣與美元脫鈎的準備；要做好全球性糧食危機爆發的準備；要做好國際反恐勢力回潮的準備。」<br />\n<br />\n在「六大準備」中，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n他指出，人民幣國際化幾年前提倡至今，反而更加退步，不論國際儲備還是國際交易中亦越來越不受歡迎。他相信未來中國還會在相當長時間內受制於美元結算系統。<br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》<br />\n<br />\n===============<br />\n<br />\n你不如話做好一個準備咪夠囉，中國要做好統治全世界嘅準備咪得囉。"},{"pid":"137b3e200580cfc66a231bfca725af463548cf75","tid":2094883,"uid":25468,"like":63,"dislike":2,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:52:25.000Z","msg":"同叫人買定棺材差唔多"},{"pid":"dabf8068d9254d0a264284a56c39dd8ff27834b6","tid":2094883,"uid":246295,"like":107,"dislike":2,"score":105,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:54:42.000Z","msg":"我想問點做好脱勾準備<br />\n做好無限通脹準備？<br />\n做好人民幣變廢紙準備？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641044066da4491833e0ec937791ac9e1c63d883","tid":2094883,"uid":8014,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:56:06.000Z","msg":"做好食草準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c1352c663040020eba53079de2e85a1a1c7de0","tid":2094883,"uid":130797,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:56:09.000Z","msg":"準備瘋狂斬殺官員同財團黎吸mp出回血技<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa52977e5411f56cdda4fc731d9633dedb48ac8","tid":2094883,"uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:57:42.000Z","msg":"要做好投降嘅準備"},{"pid":"7449d2fda181f157509e0058fca3ab8dfd56b643","tid":2094883,"uid":36775,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:59:23.000Z","msg":"Free fall <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2687ac3acb582934bd23e7ed73841e982544362","tid":2094883,"uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:59:34.000Z","msg":"共產黨成日搵pr公司同五毛喺連登同埋facebook搞分化搞內訌鬥黃 ，點解我哋唔可以反其道而行?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2094477\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2094477</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n傻仔先要求香港獨立，愛國者梗係要遊行集會要求香港警務處通緝分裂國土及顛覆國家主權的美國參議員Scott Perry<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2094418\" data-